Title: Gift Cards in Bulk
Text: I purchased 10 of these gift cards at $100 each. What you see is what you get. Each gift card came individually packaged in plastic wrap. In side the plastic wrap was a black gift envelope and orange Amazon gift card. So far, each gift card has worked and was successfully redeemed for the appropriate amount. I am pleased with my purchase and would recommend these to anyone interested in buying gift cards in bulk.

Title: Visa Giftcard
Text: I have found the best use of a Visa giftcard is to use the entire (or remaining) amount to purchase an Amazon giftcard. While Grandma thinks Visa giftcards make a great gift, too often we are left with random, small, unusable amounts. I am thankful I am able to use a Visa giftcard in it's entirety by redeeming it for an Amazon giftcard instead.
